00:12:29.460 --> 00:12:31.300
submitting hundreds of
requests trying to get records

00:12:31.300 --> 00:12:32.050
in different ways.

00:12:32.050 --> 00:12:35.605
Started submitted FOIA requests
about my FOIA requests,

00:12:35.605 --> 00:12:37.540
which we'll come back to later.

00:12:37.540 --> 00:12:40.480
I scoured-- you know, I
was scouring FOIA case law

00:12:40.480 --> 00:12:48.050
to try and find anything that
I could that would be helpful.

00:12:48.050 --> 00:12:50.890
Here's my dog and
best friend, Ihi,

00:12:50.890 --> 00:12:54.520
helping out with the
secondary literature review.

00:12:54.520 --> 00:12:57.340
Here he is again
because he's the best.

00:12:57.340 --> 00:13:03.320
And so, you know,
in the process,

00:13:03.320 --> 00:13:04.940
two things became
apparent to me.

00:13:04.940 --> 00:13:07.070
The FBI does nearly
everything in its power

00:13:07.070 --> 00:13:10.160
to avoid compliance with the
Freedom of Information Act.

00:13:10.160 --> 00:13:12.560
Indeed, if FOIA work
with some agencies is

00:13:12.560 --> 00:13:16.250
akin to trying to get customer
service over a holiday weekend

00:13:16.250 --> 00:13:19.010
from a giant telecom,
FOIA with the FBI

00:13:19.010 --> 00:13:21.980
is akin to a street fight.

00:13:21.980 --> 00:13:25.570
And number two, essential to
making FOIA work with the FBI,

00:13:25.570 --> 00:13:27.800
it was developing an
intimate familiarity

00:13:27.800 --> 00:13:29.720
with the Bureau's
FOIA-specific information

00:13:29.720 --> 00:13:32.330
storage and retrieval systems.

00:13:32.330 --> 00:13:34.430
And using the techniques
that I mentioned--

00:13:34.430 --> 00:13:36.510
the experimental
techniques that I mentioned

00:13:36.510 --> 00:13:39.110
and a bunch of others,
I did just that.

00:13:39.110 --> 00:13:41.270
And this really
started to pay off.

00:13:41.270 --> 00:13:43.556
If the FBI has x amount of
first-round dirty tricks

00:13:43.556 --> 00:13:44.930
that they use to
avoid compliance

00:13:44.930 --> 00:13:48.190
with Freedom of
Information Act requests,

00:13:48.190 --> 00:13:50.190
you know, I mapped out
a good number of them.

00:13:50.190 --> 00:13:51.720
And I started getting a
lot of documents-- in fact,

00:13:51.720 --> 00:13:53.060
thousands and
thousands of pages--

00:13:53.060 --> 00:13:55.685
about FBI campaigns against the
animal rights and environmental

00:13:55.685 --> 00:13:57.230
movements, including--

00:13:59.880 --> 00:14:02.100
oh, that's not where I
