And, you know, the FBI notes,
again in this counter-terrorism

00:33:24.220 --> 00:33:27.810
document and note
the date on it--

00:33:27.810 --> 00:33:29.520
not that long before
2000 and the FBI

00:33:29.520 --> 00:33:32.850
is spending its time looking
at puppy huggers meeting

00:33:32.850 --> 00:33:34.372
at a conference in DC.

00:33:34.372 --> 00:33:36.330
At this time, there is
no specific intelligence

00:33:36.330 --> 00:33:38.430
to suggest that any participants
in this upcoming conference

00:33:38.430 --> 00:33:40.450
