in criminal activity,

00:33:40.450 --> 00:33:45.120
but these paid lobby groups
of the biomedical research

00:33:45.120 --> 00:33:48.270
industry say that some
activists a couple of years

00:33:48.270 --> 00:33:50.550
ago got arrested protesting
outside a McDonald's when

00:33:50.550 --> 00:33:55.020
they had a conference
